Clara Horton https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Clara_Horton 0 Clara Horton (July 29, 1904 – December 4, 1976) was an American actress of the silent film era. She appeared in 88 films between 1912 and 1942. She is buried in Rose Hills Memorial Park. Clara_Horton ( July_29_,_1904 – December_4_,_1976 ) was an_American_actress of the_silent_film_era .
